<t>CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE,
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);


CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL
);


CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL
);

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);</t><s>insert into customers (customer_name, email, phone_number, address) select 'john doe', 'john.doe@example.com', '1234567890', '123 main st'</s>

    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,

    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

);

    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

);</t><s>insert into customers (customer_name, email, phone_number, address) select 'john doe', 'john.doe@example.com', '1234567890', '123 main st'</s>

    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);</t><s>insert into customers (customer_name, email, phone_number, address) select 'jane smith', 'jane.smith@example.com', '9876543210', '456 oak st'</s>

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>INSERT INTO customers (customer_name, email, phone_number, address) SELECT 'Jane Smith', 'jane.smith@example.com', '9876543210', '456 Oak St'</s>

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);</t><s>INSERT INTO customers (customer_name, email, phone_number, address) SELECT 'Jane Smith', 'jane.smith@example.com', '9876543210', '456 Oak St'</s>
<t>CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,

    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)

    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);</t><s>insert into orders (customer_id, order_date, total_amount, status) select 1, '2022-05-15', 100.50, 'pending'</s>

    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>insert into orders (customer_id, order_date, total_amount, status) select 2, '2022-05-20', 75.25, 'shipped'</s>

    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>INSERT INTO orders (customer_id, order_date, total_amount, status) SELECT 2, '2022-05-20', 75.25, 'Shipped'</s>

);

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>insert into orders (customer_id, order_date, total_amount, status) select 2, '2022-05-20', 75.25, 'shipped'</s>

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>INSERT INTO orders (customer_id, order_date, total_amount, status) SELECT 3, '2022-05-25', 150.75, 'Delivered'</s>
<t>CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,

    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,

);

    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>insert into products (product_name, price, description) select 'laptop', 800.00, 'high-performance laptop'</s>
<t>CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);</t><s>INSERT INTO products (product_name, price, description) SELECT 'Smartphone', 500.00, 'Latest smartphone model'</s>

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);</t><s>insert into products (product_name, price, description) select 'smartphone', 500.00, 'latest smartphone model'</s>

    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>INSERT INTO products (product_name, price, description) SELECT 'Smartphone', 500.00, 'Latest smartphone model'</s>

    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

);

    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);</t><s>insert into products (product_name, price, description) select 'headphones', 50.00, 'noise-cancelling headphones'</s>
<t>CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,

    address VARCHAR(255)
);

    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,

);

    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);</t><s>INSERT INTO transactions (order_id, transaction_date, payment_method) SELECT 1, '2022-05-15 10:00:00', 'Credit Card'</s>

    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);</t><s>INSERT INTO transactions (order_id, transaction_date, payment_method) SELECT 2, '2022-05-20 11:30:00', 'PayPal'</s>

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),

    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)

    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),

    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>insert into transactions (order_id, transaction_date, payment_method) select 2, '2022-05-20 11:30:00', 'paypal'</s>

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>insert into transactions (order_id, transaction_date, payment_method) select 3, '2022-05-25 09:45:00', 'cash'</s>

    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>INSERT INTO transactions (order_id, transaction_date, payment_method) SELECT 3, '2022-05-25 09:45:00', 'Cash'</s>

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);</t><s>INSERT INTO transactions (order_id, transaction_date, payment_method) SELECT 3, '2022-05-25 09:45:00', 'Cash'</s>

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>INSERT INTO contacts (customer_id, contact_name, contact_email, contact_phone) SELECT 1, 'John Doe', 'john.doe@example.com', '1234567890'</s>

    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);</t><s>insert into contacts (customer_id, contact_name, contact_email, contact_phone) select 1, 'john doe', 'john.doe@example.com', '1234567890'</s>

    customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE contacts (
    contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);</t><s>INSERT INTO contacts (customer_id, contact_name, contact_email, contact_phone) SELECT 2, 'Jane Smith', 'jane.smith@example.com', '9876543210'</s>
<t>CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    contact_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(100),
    contact_phone VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    order_date DATE,
    total_amount NUMERIC(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);</t><s>INSERT INTO contacts (customer_id, contact_name, contact_email, contact_phone) SELECT 2, 'Jane Smith', 'jane.smith@example.com', '9876543210'</s>
<t>CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    payment_method VARCHAR(20)
);

    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE orders (

    product_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,

);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_id INT REFERENCES orders(order_id),

);</t><s>insert into contacts (customer_id, contact_name, contact_email, contact_phone) select 3, 'alice johnson', 'alice.johnson@example.com', '6549873210'</s>
